11T10:31:32.000Z","msg":"間學校好似話今日無考試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw , rip<br />\n<br />\n聖文德書院中四女學生趙敏言今早遇車禍身亡。聖文德書院回應事件時表示，全體師生對事件深感悲痛，已向趙同學家人致以慰問，並提供協助，由於警方正就事件進行調查，拒對事件作揣測或下判斷，<span style=\"color: red;\">但表示學校今天並無任何考試</span>；校方已即時啟動「危機處理程序」，由教育心理學家、校內老師及學校社工輔導情緒受困擾的同學，並提供適切的協助，同時學校已向家長發信交代事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170411/56550018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170411%2F56550018&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=f8acca30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170411%2F56550018&h=0c285057\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170411/56550018</a>"},{"pid":"58fc0f0943a2cadfdcc266da4cb5034781749b39","tid":196462,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:34:33.000Z","msg":"一時無意就可以衝出馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427131ba2849722ff0a14ffd7ca48678fd8277ba","tid":196462,"uid":12449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:37:05.000Z","msg":"意外加意外 有邊個想"},{"pid":"d268eca5c8e1e288405b2116ada3875504c69012","tid":196462,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:37:25.000Z","msg":"趕唔切咪趕唔切<br />\n最多咪留班<br />\n依家搞到個司機無啦啦要坐監<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2657b76b3076a363d1c846898bc110baa60fcf","tid":196462,"uid":20828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:37:46.000Z","msg":"累人累己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲幫佢講好說話有咩用<br />\n我就一定守規矩經燈位過馬路既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁都比人撞死呢 怪我自己行衰運啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c7e1ae505f90d9baf4f79b359e161be37dde89","tid":196462,"uid":523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:41:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Hopo9V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Hopo9V.jpg&h=22633f55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果趕到行多幾步都唔得<br />\n點解唔早啲出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解點解？唔遲都遲左啦 你估人地特撚登遲？個女仔係有責任 但唔代表你班仆街可以屌人</blockquote><br />\n就算係要趕考試 都係唔應該橫過馬路<br />\n只可以話情有可原 但有原因同佢有冇錯係兩樣野黎<br />\n假如今日佢係輕傷 我諗全世界都會屌柒佢衝出馬路<br />\n但依家因為死左人（仲因為咁累到司機）<br />\n所以就有錯都唔可以罵？ <br />\n利申：同情女學生 但唔會覺得其他人冷血 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81ba271ca0eb43a6cc1d87b07925645bcbc0aaa0","tid":196462,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:45:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Hopo9V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Hopo9V.jpg&h=22633f55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果趕到行多幾步都唔得<br />\n點解唔早啲出門口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解點解？唔遲都遲左啦 你估人地特撚登遲？個女仔係有責任 但唔代表你班仆街可以屌人</blockquote><br />\n咁你又鬧人仆街？<br />\n你自己大愛撚唔代表你可以鬧唔認同你嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5d0aed00833ce8e65cd16580f3782f8f263602","tid":196462,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T10:48:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>間學校好似話今日無考試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw , rip<br />\n<br />\n聖文德書院中四女學生趙敏言今早遇車禍身亡。聖文德書院回應事件時表示，全體師生對事件深感悲痛，已向趙同學家人致以慰問，並提供協助，由於警方正就事件進行調查，拒對事件作揣測或下判斷，<span style=\"color: red;\">但表示學校今天並無任何考試</span>；校方已即時啟動「危機處理程序」，由教育心理學家、校內老師及學校社工輔導情緒受困擾的同學，並提供適切的協助，同時學校已向家長發信交代事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170411/56550018\" d